{{Top|leg}}
The '''quad-pulse laser''' was a weapon fitted to two prototype [[Delta-7 Aethersprite-class light interceptor/Legends|Delta-7 ''Aethersprite''-class light interceptors]] by [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Saesee Tiin/Legends|Saesee Tiin]].

Quad-pulse lasers were top-of-the-line armaments as of [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]], and their high rate of fire compensated for their relative weak power against conventional [[Laser cannon/Legends|laser cannons]]. [[Adi Gallia/Legends|Adi Gallia]] tested one of Tiin's prototypes, equipped with four quad-pulse lasers, during the [[Occupation of Karthakk]].

